    <title>hexo静态博客搭建</title>
    <url>/%E6%8A%80%E6%9C%AF/hexo%E9%9D%99%E6%80%81%E5%8D%9A%E5%AE%A2%E6%90%AD%E5%BB%BA/</url>
    <content><![CDATA[<h2 id="一、git、github"><a href="#一、git、github" class="headerlink" title="一、git、github"></a>一、git、github</h2><p>git安装与配置请参考 <a href="https://git-scm.com/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">git官网</a></p>
<p>静态博客这里采用github pages做托管，需要在github开启pages功能，同时以master分支作为博客页面分支</p>
<p>以source分支来存放博客原文md。</p>
<h2 id="二、nodejs、hexo安装"><a href="#二、nodejs、hexo安装" class="headerlink" title="二、nodejs、hexo安装"></a>二、nodejs、hexo安装</h2><p>nodejs安装参考<a href="https://nodejs.org/zh-cn/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">官网</a></p>
<p>hexo安装：</p>
<figure class="highlight avrasm"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">npm install -g hexo-<span class="keyword">cli</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>

<p>初始化博客</p>
<figure class="highlight ebnf"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="attribute">hexo init blog</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>

<p>生成博客</p>
<figure class="highlight shell"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">--新建博客</span><br><span class="line">hexo new post &lt;postname&gt;</span><br><span class="line">--清除public目录</span><br><span class="line">hexo clean</span><br><span class="line">--生成public目录</span><br><span class="line">hexo g</span><br><span class="line">--上传部署</span><br><span class="line">hexo d</span><br><span class="line">--本地查看</span><br><span class="line">hexo s</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>

<h2 id="三、换电脑搭建"><a href="#三、换电脑搭建" class="headerlink" title="三、换电脑搭建"></a>三、换电脑搭建</h2><p>master分支只存放博文的html，需要新建source分支存放博文</p>
<p>备份blog原有配置</p>
<figure class="highlight reasonml"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="module-access"><span class="module"><span class="identifier">_config</span>.</span></span>yml</span><br><span class="line"> package.json</span><br><span class="line"> scaffolds/</span><br><span class="line"> source/</span><br><span class="line"> themes/</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>

<p>安装工具初始化</p>
<figure class="highlight properties"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="attr">npm</span> <span class="string">install hexo-cli -g</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="attr">hexo</span> <span class="string">init blog</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="attr">cd</span> <span class="string">blog</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>

<p>将第一步备份的文件替换自动生成的文件</p>
<h2 id="四、主题"><a href="#四、主题" class="headerlink" title="四、主题"></a>四、主题</h2><p>推荐两个主题</p>
<p><a href="https://github.com/theme-next/hexo-theme-next" target="_blank" rel="noopener">next</a>:hexo下最火的主题</p>
<p><a href="https://github.com/tufu9441/maupassant-hexo" target="_blank" rel="noopener">maupassant</a>:Maupassant最初是由<a href="https://github.com/pagecho/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Cho</a>大神为<a href="http://typecho.org/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Typecho</a>平台设计开发的一套响应式模板，体积只有20KB.特点就是简洁，快！</p>
]]></content>
